reviewText: What do I need to say that you don't already know about these movies.
Brought me out of the doom and loom to realizing I missed laughing, this item Thanks, enjoyed by every one
I needed a new version of Old School because my previous version was worn down from overuse.  This was the perfect fit in a blu-ray format for me.  I'm happy with the purchase and price was right.
i like it when they come out with double or triple feature movies cause it helps with space to store them
It can't get better than these two movies in one package.  This is a must buy for anyone looking for a good laugh.
